title: New Photo - Dutch Photography Talent 2015.pdf
description:
New Photo. Dutch Photography Talent 2015
English | PDF | 114 pages | 12 MB

New is a book, a catalogue, a style-guide, an annual featuring the best 100 emerging Dutch photographers. New is a platform bringing Dutch based photography talents to the attention of galleries, museums, commercial and photography agencies, media companies and institutions that work with imagery
